# Git Initial Configuration

## Instructions

1. Open Git Bash
2. `git config --global user.name "Andrei.Popescu"`  
   - This command sets the global username for Git to "Andrei.Popescu".
3. `git config --global user.email "Andrei.Popescu@gmail.com"`  
   - This command sets the global email address for Git to "Andrei.Popescu@gmail.com".
4. `git config --global --list`  
   - This command displays a list of all the global configuration settings currently set in Git.
